---
import HeroFloaters from "../components/react/HeroFloaters.tsx";
---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative flex min-h-svh w-full flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
>
  <HeroFloaters client:load />

  {/* Viewport-pinned: min-h-svh with centred content, so the section rhythm
      (`py-section`) deliberately does NOT apply here — the space Clients sees
      below is (svh − content) / 2 from the centring, not this padding. The py
      below is only a floor for short viewports, where the content would
      otherwise touch the edges. See the rhythm note in styles/global.css. */}
  <div
    class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex w-full max-w-8xl flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 text-center tablet:px-8 desktop:px-12"
  >
    <h1 class="max-w-[15ch] text-h1 text-balance">
      El diseño como herramienta de negocio
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 max-w-[42ch] text-p-lg text-pretty text-muted">
      Diseñamos sistemas visuales que aportan dirección, fortalecen el
      posicionamiento y potencian el valor percibido de tu marca.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10">
      {
        /* Pill CTA: on hover the arrow circle slides in from the right and the
        button expands to make room for it. */
      }
      <a
        href="#cta"
        class="group relative inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-primary py-4 pr-9 pl-9 text-p-lg font-medium text-text-inverse transition-[padding] duration-300 ease-out desktop:hover:pr-[4.5rem] focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-surface focus-visible:outline-none motion-reduce:transition-none"
      >
        <span>Hablemos de tu marca</span>
        <span
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="pointer-events-none absolute top-1/2 right-2 grid size-12 translate-x-[160%] -translate-y-1/2 place-items-center rounded-full bg-white text-primary opacity-0 transition-[translate,opacity] duration-300 ease-out desktop:group-hover:translate-x-0 desktop:group-hover:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"
        >
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="size-5"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
